Ranger Help for: ranhist
========================

SYNTAX:      ranhist
             rhist
USAGE:       Anywhere

SUMMARY:
This command displays the recent history of the Ranger guild chat
channel. It shows the last several messages sent on the 'ran' channel,
including timestamps and who sent each message. This is useful for
catching up on conversations you may have missed while away. The
'rhist' command is a shorter alias for 'ranhist'.
